metadata.name: Baked Frenz
metadata.description: 'Baked Frenz' portrays characters in vivid colors, exploring how people ease their pain through different coping methods. The contrast of bright colors and dark undertones symbolizes the conflicting aspects of human experiences and how we can mask our feelings with happiness. It explores the complexity of the human mind and the challenges we all encounter. It suggests that amidst the darkness, there are moments of joy and positivity, showcasing the polarities in our lives.
